Jumbo Golden PoohPooh figures dropping tomorrow on @niftygateway 2ft Electroplated Resin figures! edition of 10! Ranked Bidding (10 highest bidders)

#art #physical #designertoy #sculpture #nft #nifty #viral #crypto #alexsolis #viral #thefuture #blockchain #shiny #rare #fungibletoken #poohpoohfigure

Icon Unmasked #iconsunmasked 

Monday on @niftygateway 

Three will require you to own a previous icon unmasked NFT the other three will be open edition for 5 minutes! 

Which one should we make into a physical figure?

node.text:
Excited to show you guys a new kind of NFT project launching with my collection July 12th on @niftygateway , NFT holders will send in an image (selfie/art/doodle/petphoto) of your choosing, you will own the initial NFT + become apart of the final art piece and help it come to life! The final image; along with everyone's images will populate the rotating planet and you will become apart of a unique art project. 
I'll be uploading more information and details as we get closer to the launch date. 

So so excited to be able to involve everyone that supports my work into the artwork itself, because I've wouldnt have gotten this far without you guys! 🖤🤍🖤🤍

#art #you #foryou #thankyou #artists #death #life #together #collaboration #light #3d #zbrush #keyshot #sculpture #alexsolis @gemini
